{"tid":142330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"銀行經理墮樓喪命 留遺書給妻女「我支持唔到落去」","createTime":"2017-03-03T16:00:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-04T11:19:22.000Z","uid":1886,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1f644c3445bc4b77de6a26c454998fdeb2aed8b3","tid":142330,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T16:00:28.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>銀行經理墮樓喪命 留遺書給妻女「我支持唔到落去」<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170303/56380119\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170303%2F56380119&d=I5RPnmyQkmy%2BYB%2FsDyc%2Bv9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=9a83c068\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170303%2F56380119&h=f185d3eb\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170303/56380119</a></strong></span></div><br />\n<br />\n荃灣海壩街54號滿樂大廈安寧樓，下午3時許，一名姓高男子由高處墮下，倒卧對開空地當場不治。警方封鎖現場調查，撿獲死者遺下的物品，發現一封遺書，內容提及「我真的支持唔到落去，我愛您們，對唔住，爸爸」，警方正了解原因。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170303/large/1488532748_c6d6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170303%2Flarge%2F1488532748_c6d6.jpg&h=3f4e2167&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(詹家志攝)<br />\n<br />\n據了解，死者在元朗一間銀行任職經理，今早原定上班，但他未有出現，未幾他發短訊予朋友透露尋死，朋友大驚通知其妻，事主妻子中午時分往旺角報警，至下午3時接獲警方通知，男事主已從荃灣跳樓身亡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170303/large/1488527824_3139.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170303%2Flarge%2F1488527824_3139.jpg&h=a130feac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方封鎖現場調查。(詹家志攝)<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288"},{"pid":"7b0de5e0922f35e3d8c4f1f8361841cba01ab6e4","tid":142330,"uid":26354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T16:03:07.000Z","msg":"建行？"},{"pid":"ec1e38ec70d720a9c00e02bcab2364e566a8733b","tid":142330,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T16:04:36.000Z","msg":"交唔到數？"},{"pid":"bee74e1fefadf2dfc6d845119e719833e4492880","tid":142330,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T16:04:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>建行？</blockquote><br />\n一家三口，老婆唔做野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86a65f1299d980fea3e3e4660d54be63f721481f","tid":142330,"uid":26354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T16:09:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>建行？</blockquote><br />\n一家三口，老婆唔做野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n三四年前好似調左個姓高去建行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cd97ddd35b070846b68dd991dbd5399b1157402","tid":142330,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T16:34:02.000Z","msg":"近年匪資銀行好多分店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f41958bee19a887d6442cb991038a6dd6d5ace7c","tid":142330,"uid":30578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T16:35:47.000Z","msg":"教育問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96b8f544dcb7f85aef700ac61e5f9dbf38176890","tid":142330,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T16:36:05.000Z","msg":"慘"},{"pid":"6c2969c6c2f10a5e547af7dbdd3ea14b00785a12","tid":142330,"uid":9541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T16:41:39.000Z","msg":"交通既"},{"pid":"27604badcda87c40856d4147e22d901b925c4152","tid":142330,"uid":9541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201